A RESOLUTION
1 Commending the Miss Georgia Peach Scholarship Pageant and congratulating the 2024
2 Georgia Peach Queens; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the peach has a long been a nationally recognized symbol for the State of
4 Georgia; and
5 WHEREAS, the Georgia peach industry has played a significant role in the economic growth
6 and prosperity of our state, and Georgia ranks third in the nation in the annual production of
7 peaches; and
8 WHEREAS, the Miss Georgia Peach Scholarship Pageant originated in Peach County,
9 Georgia, in 1982 thanks to the Pilot Club of Fort Valley, who conceived the pageant for the
10 purpose of having Ambassadors of the famous Georgia Peach Festival held in June each
11 year; and
12 WHEREAS, this annual pageant is open statewide to girls 4 to 24 for the purpose of building
13 self-confidence while acknowledging those who make a positive contribution to the
14 community; and
