15 WHEREAS, in connection with this celebration, five very fine young ladies were crowned
16 as the 2024 Peach Queens, including Miss Georgia Peach, Charleigh Harper; Teen Miss
17 Georgia Peach, Mia Loyd; Junior Miss Georgia Peach, Kendall Bella Gaines; Little Miss
18 Georgia Peach, Skye Harris; and Tiny Miss Georgia Peach, Ellie James Young; and
19 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this festival and its representatives be
20 recognized by this body.
21 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
22 the members of this body commend the Miss Georgia Peach Scholarship Pageant for
23 promoting the importance of this agricultural product of Georgia and congratulate the 2024
24 Georgia Peach Queens.
25 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
26 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
27 Board of Directors of the Miss Georgia Peach Scholarship Pageant.
